OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FA senior PSNI officer has denied
OL,7,Ftelling police witnesses "what to say"
OL,8,Fwhen giving evidence to the Noah
OL,9,FDonohoe inquest.
OL,11,FPSNI Detective Chief Inspector
OL,12,FPhillips, who was a senior
OL,13,Finvestigating officer in the high-
OL,14,Fprofile missing person investigation,
OL,15,Fsaid he "made no mention at all" of
OL,16,Fthe schoolboy's coat to a junior
OL,17,Fofficer, who could not explain why he
OL,18,Fsaid in evidence that he had been
OL,19,Ftasked with searching for it.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUoD@fO]wD@IOUwD@`O]
