PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781698292
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FIn March, PSNI Constable Wharry told
OL,7,Fthe inquest, now in its 20th week,
OL,8,Fthat on June 25 2020, four days after
OL,9,FNoah disappeared, he was tasked with
OL,10,Fassisting CID with the arrest of a man
OL,11,Fat a flat in Belfast.
OL,13,FThe man, Daryl Paul, previously
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to stealing a rucksack
OL,15,Fcontaining Noah's laptop and school
OL,16,Fbooks.
OL,18,FMr Wharry told the court he had been
OL,19,Fadvised that Noah's laptop, bag and
OL,20,Fgreen coat were in Paul's possession.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781698292
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FBrenda Campbell KC, representing
OL,7,FNoah's mother, Fiona, asked him: "Did
OL,8,Fyou understand before you got into the
OL,9,Fwitness box today that a concern was
OL,10,Fthe failure of the police to look for
OL,11,FNoah's green coat?"
OL,13,FThe officer said he had been "briefed"
OL,14,Fat Musgrave Street police station
OL,15,Fbefore he gave evidence that there had
OL,16,Fbeen concerns about the coat.
OL,18,FAt Belfast Coroner's Court on Monday,
OL,19,FMr Phillips read jurors a statement
OL,20,Ffrom himself dated 20 April 2026.
OL,26,@oD@bOUsD@SO]uD@^OUuD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/17
