PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781698292
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FHe said the "routine for PSNI
OL,7,Fwitnesses has been to meet myself and
OL,8,Fmy team in Musgrave" before giving
OL,9,Fevidence to the inquest.
OL,11,FHe said police witnesses get copies of
OL,12,Fhard evidence and are accompanied to
OL,13,Fand from court.
OL,15,FMr Phillips said the majority of
OL,16,Fpolice witnesses have consulted PSNI
OL,17,Fcouncil, led by Donal Lunny KC, before
OL,18,Ftheir court appearance, sometimes more
OL,19,Fthan once.
OL,26,@nD@MOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/17
