OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781698292
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FDiscussing his meeting with Detective
OL,7,FInspector Cunningham and Constable
OL,8,FWharry, he said he told the latter he
OL,9,Fcould expect to be a "fairly short
OL,10,Fwitness" on a "fairly discrete issue"
OL,11,Fof body-worn footage.
OL,13,F"I gave no consideration to the matter
OL,14,Fof the search overall being put to him
OL,15,Fnor was it discussed," his statement
OL,16,Fread.
OL,18,FHe added: "At no time did I tell
OL,19,Feither of the parties what to say.
OL,26,@qD@VOUrD@HO]rD@OOUrD@eO]uD@AOUwD@VO]zD@
OL,26,AKOU
