OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781698292
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,F"I did not discuss the nature of the
OL,7,Fsearch with Con Wharry and made no
OL,8,Fmention at all of Noah's green coat."
OL,10,FEarlier on Monday, the inquest heard
OL,11,Ffrom PSNI Detective Inspector
OL,12,FMcCartan, who was a detective
OL,13,Fconstable in 2020 when he led the
OL,14,Fhouse-to-house searches conducted to
OL,15,Ffind the missing schoolboy.
OL,17,FAs house-to-house co-ordinator, he
OL,18,Fsaid his task was to attend addresses
OL,19,Fto identify potential witnesses.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/17
