CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781698292
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FThe parameters for the search included
OL,7,Fhomes on a number of streets in the
OL,8,FNorthwood Drive area near the culvert
OL,9,Fwhere Noah's body was later found.
OL,11,FMr McCartan said full resident house-
OL,12,Fto-house forms were not completed for
OL,13,Feach visit as it would be "hugely time-
OL,14,Fconsuming", officers instead using a
OL,15,Fquestionnaire form that Mr McCartan
OL,16,Fhimself produced and he said was
OL,17,F"considerably quicker".
OL,26,@uD@[OUvD@JO]yD@AOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/17
