CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781698292
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FMs Campbell questioned the officer
OL,7,Fabout the process for flagging any
OL,8,F"thematic" issues uncovered in the
OL,9,Fsearches.
OL,11,FMr McCartan said he collated a
OL,12,Fspreadsheet that was updated at the
OL,13,Fend of each day by officers involved
OL,14,Fin searches, that the investigating
OL,15,Fofficers and CCTV and witness co-
OL,16,Fordinators would have had access to.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/17
