OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781698292
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FMs Campbell highlighted "two
OL,7,Fneighbours", one referring to "a back
OL,8,Fdoor handle being tried around 3am"
OL,9,Fand another referring to screams heard
OL,10,Fin the area on the Sunday night when
OL,11,FNoah was last seen.
OL,13,FThe inquest was then shown a
OL,14,Fquestionnaire from a house in
OL,15,FNorthwood Road where the resident
OL,16,Freported hearing "noises" and a
OL,17,Fcomment reading "back of house".
OL,26,@nD@YOUoD@KO]oD@_OUpD@cO]xD@ROUxD@YO]yD@
OL,26,AQOUyD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
