PN,41911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781698292
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FMr McCartan said the officer who
OL,7,Ffilled out that form "would have
OL,8,Fpressed" the residents if there was a
OL,9,F"specific noise" and also said he
OL,10,Fcould not say "for definite" the back-
OL,11,Fof-the-house comment referred to where
OL,12,Fthe resident felt the noise was coming
OL,13,Ffrom.
OL,15,FThe officers' spreadsheet was then
OL,16,Fshown to the court and beside one
OL,17,Fhouse number a comment was written
OL,18,F"misper naked, deserted bike and
OL,19,Fwalked up back of house".
OL,26,@oD@VOUpD@HO]qD@AOUqD@PO]rD@OOUrD@\O]zD@
OL,26,AAOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/17
