OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781698292
OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FAsked if Mr McCartan thought the
OL,7,Fofficer was telling him the residents
OL,8,F"saw misper naked", he replied "I
OL,9,Fcan't answer that", adding "I didn't
OL,10,Fquiz (the officer) on what she had put
OL,11,Fon each of those boxes".
OL,13,FLater, Ms Campbell said the
OL,14,Fspreadsheet implied "on one reading" a
OL,15,Fwitness who saw Noah naked and asked
OL,16,F"whose job is it to flag that to make
OL,17,Fsure somebody's going out there to get
OL,18,Fthat statement?".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@RO]pD@`OUqD@RO]qD@\OUsD@WO]vD@
OL,26,AUOUvD@dO]xD@AOUzD@PO]
