OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FMr McCartan said it would have been
OL,7,Freviewed by CCTV and the witness co-
OL,8,Fordinator after being added to the
OL,9,Fspreadsheet.
OL,11,FPressed on the fact there is no
OL,12,Fstatement from that witness from 2020,
OL,13,Fthe officer said it is "not for me to
OL,14,Fcollate witness statements", his job
OL,15,Fat that time was trying to figure out
OL,16,F"where Noah was and where he had gone
OL,17,Fto next".
OL,26,@uD@XOUvD@[O]xD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/17
