OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FThe jurors later saw a house-to-house
OL,7,Fquestionnaire where the residents
OL,8,Fdescribed a "tall" boy with "dark
OL,9,Fhair" and seeing him "take his top off
OL,10,Fand put it on the wall" at the address
OL,11,Fwhere some of Noah's clothes were
OL,12,Flater found.
OL,14,FMs Campbell put it to the officer that
OL,15,Fwhen Noah was at that address at
OL,16,FNorthwood Drive "at least two people
OL,17,Fhad eyes on him and we have statements
OL,18,Ffrom neither of them", asking Mr
OL,19,FMcCartan "your response is the same,
OL,20,Fnot your responsibility, not your
OL,21,Fremit?", to which he responded "yes".
