OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FShe showed the court an entry on the
OL,7,Fspreadsheet beside a redacted house
OL,8,Fnumber with the comment "strange
OL,9,Factivity", which Mr McCartan said he
OL,10,Fcould not elaborate on.
OL,12,FMs Campbell asked "has anyone ever
OL,13,Fasked you to?", to which he replied
OL,14,F"no".
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@IO]tD@SOUuD@NO]vD@AOUvD@DO]
