OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FLater, under questioning by Mr Lunny,
OL,7,FMr McCartan agreed that the
OL,8,Finformation on searches in the
OL,9,Fspreadsheet was "accessible by any
OL,10,Fofficer during that week" and if they
OL,11,F"had any questions" they would be able
OL,12,Fto contact him.
OL,14,FMr Lunny asked if investigating
OL,15,Fofficers would "know where to go to
OL,16,Fget that information" if they had
OL,17,Fquestions such as those posed by Ms
OL,18,FCampbell, to which Mr McCartan said:
OL,19,F"Yes."
OL,26,@qD@QOUrD@YO]sD@AOUsD@SO]wD@POUxD@UO]{D@
OL,26,AAOU{D@FO]
