OL,3,CSenior PSNI officer denies telling
OL,4,Cwitnesses 'what to say' at inquest
OL,6,FPolice logs were also seen by the
OL,7,Fjury, showing that by June 26, 187
OL,8,Fwitnesses had been identified by
OL,9,Fpolice.
OL,11,FBy July 9 2020, more than 200
OL,12,Fpotential witnesses had been
OL,13,Fidentified before being honed to 13
OL,14,F"significant witnesses".
